nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Pre-production discovery
\series default
:
 Critical and High severity flaws identified during testing shall be fully remediated prior to production deployment.
 No system containing an unmitigated Critical or High severity flaw shall be accepted into production.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Post-deployment discovery
\series default
:
 All severity timelines shall conform to the schedule established in 
